title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Tension Tests, Impact Tests, Hardness Tests, Bending and Torsion Tests, Calibration of Proving Rings, Fatigue Tests, Strain Gage Experiments, Study of Photo-elastic Bench, Calibration of Photo-elastic materials, Wear of Materials.
